        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The Commission establishes Docket Nos. MC2015-63 and CP2015-94 to consider the matters raised in each docket.",
        "bbox": [
          0.36278195545331265,
          0.6613372094410074,
          0.6372180362503296,
